::Striker::

Striker raises an eyebrow, looking at Spears as she steps back from him and 
sits down. He was a bit surprised at her reaction, but panic brought on 
strange reactions.

"Relax. We're at 0 feet above sea level. In other words floating till we 
regain energy," he grins then, "You have no fear of floating, do you?"
